title: Bach, JS - Brandenburg Concertos - Egarr, AAM
description:
Bach: Brandenburg Concertos.

JS Bach's six Brandenburg Concertos, recorded by the Academy of Ancient Music under their new director, Richard Egarr, and released by Harmonia Mundi in 2009. This is my personal favourite period instrument performance of these works. It makes an interesting contrast to Hogwood's 1980s recording of the Brandenburgs with this same orchestra.

Please enjoy.

MP3 @ 320
